 1 年以下有期徒刑、拘役或 1 萬 5\r\n千元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/110%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%e4%b8%8a%2c167%2c20220915%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,110,審簡上,167,20220915,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"審簡上","JNO":"167","JDATE":"20220915","JTITLE":"妨害名譽"}